values:
I've noticed that over the past couple of years of my life that I've wanted to be normal because of my disablity I Tylor Evans wanted to be everyone else to be different and my recent surgurys have changed that view from the day I was born I have been different by all means I should not even be here!!! I realized last night That I flatlined at birth and then I died on the operation table during my hip sugury!! I have lost friends my homie Nick pass away trying to be the hero tried to save his dads girlfriend life the house fire engulfed the house and he made it to the door TO THE DOOR!!! and the roof fell on him and he burned to death an other homie Seth Bailey died because his girl dumped him he went to the look out and drank and pass out suffocated because he had a tube in his throat and he needed oxygen he died in his sleep

my question is Why!! they had a reason and didn't live to see it, and yet I lived and yet I feel I've accomplished what was needed I've spoke for people who couldn't, heard for the deaf, and seen for the blind, moved for the motionless,

and yet what now?

people remember for those less fortunate than you because if you don't people won't remember you

Ok here is how it goes I find out certain ppl have had things to say since i was i delaware and well these ppl were really good friends and i would have taken a bullet for em but since they want to play the damn game of "I'm your friend...Till you walk away" I'm gonna make a BIG change in person...BELIEVE ME!!!!!!! you'll see it
back from delaware sunburn? yes, new shit? yes, any numbers? I KNEW I'D FORGET SOMETHING!!!!!!!!
delaware here i come!!!!!!!! beach baby yes!!!!!! hahaha

Hey all, Man I want to leave my folks man their constantly tormenting me!!! some of the things I understand, others I don't, but I do intend to leave. 

I just have to get through with Shriners Hospital, in KY. I've talked to my step mom she says she will help out sooo... anyway as to where i want to move to it will prolly be near home at first but after, it prolly somewhere 4 hours away (And no cali it's not waynesboro)just in case she reads this 

Cali is a friend.

Anyway I'm out all bye bye

I know I haven't wrote in this thing in forever but i've been building a myspace so it will prolly b a while
http://www.myspace.com/12925303
put that in your url and smoke it!!!!!!!!!!

Well I'm getting S.S.I checks now from the government, $579.00 Wohoooo!!!! Anyway I made a new Myspace, at www.Myspace.com (Just In case your interested) and found 2 old friends of mine hopefully they will write me back, anyway I'm tired I'm going back to bed,

I'll write soon

Finally!!! a place where I can post my thoughts, ideas, belief's, and what not and noooo one can tell me I'm crazy. Anyway my name is Tylor, and I've had a lot of sh!t happen recently. I've had surgery on my hips and ankle but don't feel bad. Anyone that knows me will tell you I'm not worried about it, and that I'm usually hard headed, but that's just me. Anyway hopefully you all will welcome me into this deal and W/E. 

Peace all!!!!
